name: Jennifer Tong

last_movies.title: 女巫前线：塞勒姆要塞 第二季

introduction: Jennifer Tong is a Leo-nominated actor from Vancouver, B.C., Canada. Born and raised on the west coast, she started performing at a young age. Exploring dance, singing and musical theatre as she grew up, she finally found acting as her main passion. Starting in theatre, she was a part of stage productions such as Annie, Christmas Carol, Harvey amongst many. She discovered her love for film while attending the Acting for Stage and Screen program at Capilano University. Ever since graduation, she has been on multiple stages around the city, working with a variety of theatre companies. She is fully immersed in the film industry, whether it be as a recurring character on a Netflix show, a supporting role on a feature movie or a guest star on a CW series. When she's not acting, you can find her discovering restaurants and cafés, swimming in the ocean or eating ridiculous amounts of raspberry liquorice.
